name: COBRANZA ALUMNOS
query:
SELECT
 student as "Student:Link/Student:200",
 student_name as "Student Name::200",
 tabStudent Batch Student.student_mobile_number as "student_mobile_number:200",
 sum(paid_amount) as "Paid Amount:Currency:150",
 sum(outstanding_amount) as "Outstanding Amount:Currency:150",
 sum(grand_total) as "Grand Total:Currency:150"
FROM
 `tabFees`,`tabStudent Batch Student` 
GROUP BY
 student
